2BFC6FE8.Line6.101CAF: Yes, I - (winces) I believe I will be, if only I might rest a spell and get some food in me.

8EB34783.Line1.101CAF: Thank the High Heavens! I was starting to think someone might never come along.

DEE97350.VoiceDir1.101CAF: Grateful and a bit winded; he just jogged to safety.

F6220138.Line15.101CAF: A gracious offer. I'll do my best not to slow you down.
